    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-07-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-07-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="135"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d135">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Señor Mitre y Vedia</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Argentine Legation in the United States,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-07-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 17, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary:</hi> I have just received your esteemed note
                    of the 11th instant, in reply to mine of the 9th, informing me that you think it
                    would be better for both governments to have the affair to which my despatch
                    relates settled in Buenos Ayres, and that you have instructed Mr. Asboth to
                    confer with the Argentine government immediately, hoping they will have good
                    cause of satisfaction.</p>
                <p>In reply, all that I have to say is, that I will inform my government of that
                    determination, hoping the result may be as you desire.</p>
                <p>I remain your attentive and obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>B. MITRE Y VEDIA.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
